data.description: Pristine 1-story in the peaceful community of Marine Creek Ranch! Featuring 3 generously sized bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms and an office - this home is the perfect space for family and friends to gather. Upon entering, you'll immediately feel at home. The interior has tasteful finishes that create a warm and welcoming ambiance. The living room includes a cozy wood-burning fireplace and the kitchen is a chef's dream - boasting ample cabinetry, granite counters top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, double ovens, gas cooktop and an island that is perfect for whipping up your favorite meals. Outside, you'll find a large backyard with plenty of room to play, relax or entertain. The covered patio is the perfect spot for hosting barbecues or enjoying a quiet evening under the stars. Schedule your showing today!
